snippet.title: Minecraft x The Incredibles DLC
snippet.description:
It’s a whole family of Supers! Join the fun with Violet, Jack-Jack, Dash, their Incredible parents and Frozone in this super DLC. Take on fearsome foes like the Underminer and Screenslaver, explore iconic locations such as Municiberg, and… hey, where’s my super suit? It’s in the Dressing Room, as a free Character Creator item!

Find the DLC here: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=5e1271b9-484c-4a1d-a9f4-5c919e8a0bbb
